Package: a2munge
Title: Synchronoss Advanced Analytics Data Munging R Package
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Chris", "Haarstick", email = "Chris.Haarstick@synchronoss.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Data munging functionality to support Synchronoss Advanced Analytics applications. Includes functions for data ingestion, data preperation, data transformation and data enrichment. The package supports both base R and Spark DataFrame objects. 
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0)
